But I started thinking and looking for ideas (it took a long time) and in the end, in the last 10 days decided to make a hand-carved "Metaverse" World using wood material, and inside it contains several games that are often played in gambling. There is Mr. Roo in the Box using Virtual Reality (VR) Glasses welcoming players.1. Spin Board2. Slot Machine3. Domino Cards4.
